original_title: 2008 Sound Horizon Triumph of Territorial Expansion II
overview: Bonus live DVD from 『Triumph 』 Photo Collection.  Features live performances from Sound Horizon Live Tour 2007 "The Great Invasion of Territorial Expansion II & Triumph".  Recorded live on September 23 at Nakano Sunplaza and on October 27 at Shinagawa Stellar Ball.
title: 2008 Sound Horizon Triumph of Territorial Expansion II
